  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Provides an optional base class for an <see cref="T:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.IRealtimeClient" /> that passes through calls to another instance.
            </summary>
    <remarks>
            This is recommended as a base type when building clients that can be chained around an underlying <see cref="T:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.IRealtimeClient" />.
            The default implementation simply passes each call to the inner client instance.
            </remarks>
